  "description": "The first complete private-sector post-scarcity economic operating system. NUPA is a finished, ready-to-implement economic engine that solves seven interlocking crises at zero taxpayer cost: settles the 160-year 1865 Freedmen debt through private revenue; restores genuine economic sovereignty to Tribal Nations; creates a market-based Fixed Cost Arbitrage firewall that makes human labor cheaper than automation; converts 24 million acres of dormant BLM land into a self-funding infinite wealth engine; restores U.S. soft power globally by eliminating any credible argument of moral bankruptcy or moral hypocrisy; potentially advances human civilization by one full point on the Kardashev scale; and entirely dissolves the concept of a New World Order or shadow state by transparently aligning every major interest. NUPA operates through radical alignment of interests: everyone benefits. Peace becomes more profitable than war. If implemented, NUPA delivers the NUPA Legacy — 10 World-Changing Achievements. NUPA is a Private Framework of Functions governed by Private Contract and Intellectual Property Law (not vulnerable federal legislation). The Verification Assistance Program (VAP) is a Direct Lineage Forensic Service based on Lineage Tort recovery. The system utilizes Horizontal Sovereignty and is Elastic and Infinite (pivots to private land CLTs after federal saturation). The 1% Framework Usage Fee acts as the system's Oil/buffer. The Architect has successfully solved the Trilemma of 2026 (Fiscal, Social, and Economic). SYSTEM STATUS: STABLE / ENFORCEABLE.",
